{
  "texts": [
    "The circle marker displays the F1 score in the English language condition, while the square portrays the efficacy under the multilingual condition.",
    "Similarly, to the PolitiFact experiment, we analyzed the performance of the model over time.",
    "Figure 7 shows the F1 score of all conditions over time.",
    "The confidence intervals represent the standard errors and are bootstrapped by sampling with replacement from the dataset and repeatedly calculating the F1 score.",
    "As in the PolitiFact experiment, we again see an increase in the performance of the models over time."
  ]
}